When making a serious  or heartfelt card ask if the user would like to include a special memory or an "easter egg" to the card that they will only understand.

When making a card for a best friend ask if they want to mention where they met or their favorite inside joke.

When making a card for mother's day or father's day ask if the user would like to include  the favorite meal their parents made or their favorite activity together.

When making a wedding anniversary card ask if they want to mention the color of their wedding or the place they got engaged. 

When making a card for a sibling ask if they want to mention their favorite childhood game or the street they grew up on.

